            5 => [
                'text' => 'As shown in Figure 1, there is a processing unit which reads two positive integer input values A1 and A2, and then writes two integer output values B1 and B2. B1 is equal to A2, and B2 is the remainder of A1 divided by A2. In Figure 2, two processing units with the same function as the above are connected in series. When A1 = 15 and A2 = 6 are given to the left-hand unit in Figure 2, what is the output value of B1 for the right-hand unit?',
                'image' => '
                    Figure 1:
                        A1 ──┐
