                                              ├── [Unit] ── B1 = ?
                                              │
                         (from left unit B1) ──┘
                    
                    First unit: 15 ÷ 6 = 2 remainder 3, so B1=6, B2=3
                    Second unit: A1=6 (from B1), A2=3 (from B2)
                    6 ÷ 3 = 2 remainder 0, so B1=3, B2=0
