                    |   | R  W  X                 | R  W  X                 | R  W  X         |
                    +---+-------------------------+-------------------------+-----------------+
                    | a | *  *  *                 | *  *  -                 | -  -  *         |
                    | b | *  *  -                 | *  -  *                 | -  -  *         |
                    | c | *  -  *                 | *  *  -                 | -  -  *         |
                    | d | *  -  *                 | -  -  *                 | -  -  *         |
