                'text' => 'There are five (5) lamps arranged in line. Each of them can be turned on and off independently. How many patterns are there where two (2) or more lamps are turned on? Here, the pattern where all lamps are turned on is counted as one (1) and the pattern where any one of them is turned on is counted as five (5).',
