                'Step 3: Option a is correct'
            ],
            'key_concepts' => ['CPU Architecture', 'Word Size', '32-bit vs 64-bit'],
            'difficulty' => 'Easy'
        ],
        14 => [
            'explanation' => 'A dual system uses two identical systems running in parallel, comparing results to verify correctness. If one fails, the other continues, providing fault tolerance.',
