            'key_concepts' => ['Database Transactions', 'ACID', 'Transaction Logs', 'Recovery'],
            'difficulty' => 'Medium'
        ],
        30 => [
            'explanation' => 'To protect all devices with the firewall, the router with firewall must be placed between the Internet and all internal devices. Option A shows this configuration: Internet → Router(FW) → Hub → Devices.',
