    14 => [
        'explanation' => 'Availability: Series (A) = a²; Parallel (B) = 1-(1-a)²; Combined (C) = [1-(1-a)²]×a. For a<1, B > C > A.',
        'steps' => [
            'Step 1: Calculate availability formulas (a = device availability):',
            '   A (series): a × a = a²',
            '   B (parallel): 1 - (1-a)² = 2a - a²',
            '   C: [1 - (1-a)²] × a = (2a - a²) × a = 2a² - a³',
            'Step 2: For typical a=0.9:',
            '   A = 0.81',
            '   B = 0.99',
